data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming spacious beautiful 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath Townhome located centrally next to Countryway & Westchase subdivisions and only 15 minutes away from the airport and all local beaches.    This large end unit holds access to the Upper Tampa Bay trail right out your front door.    This location is conveniently located less than a mile from Alonso High School with convenient shopping centers located a short distance such as Target, Michael's, Starbucks, and Petco.    Step inside to find plush carpet in the bedrooms, luxurious hard wood flooring in the spacious living areas, and beautiful tile in the kitchen and bathrooms to include a large garden tub in the master bath. The tile roof and AC unit are both less than 1 to 3 years old, ensuring worry-free living.    Enjoy the serene atmosphere of the dog-friendly community, complete with a private cabana and pool for relaxation. Low HOA fees include water, exterior pest control, and lawn maintenance.    Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful townhome your own!
